OL,6,FChelsea and FIFA are investigating
OL,7,Fafter midfielder Enzo Fernandez
OL,8,Fapologised for an "offensive" video
OL,9,Fposted on his Instagram account.
OL,11,FThe French Football Federation said on
OL,12,FTuesday it would file a legal
OL,13,Fcomplaint alleging "racially offensive
OL,14,Fand discriminatory remarks" were made
OL,15,Fby Argentina players following their
OL,16,FCopa America victory over Colombia.
