OL,3,CChelsea and FIFA investigating after
OL,4,CEnzo Fernandez posts 'offensive' video
OL,6,FThe complaint follows footage that was
OL,7,Fposted by Chelsea midfielder
OL,8,FFernandez, which appeared to show him
OL,9,Fand his team-mates chanting about the
OL,10,FFrance team as they celebrated their 1-
OL,11,F0 win in Sunday's final.
OL,13,FFernandez put a statement on his
OL,14,FInstagram account on Tuesday night,
OL,15,Fsaying: "I want to apologise sincerely
OL,16,Ffor a video posted on my Instagram
OL,17,Fchannel during the national team
OL,18,Fcelebrations.
