OL,6,F"The song includes highly offensive
OL,7,Flanguage and there is absolutely no
OL,8,Fexcuse for these words.
OL,10,F"I stand against discrimination in all
OL,11,Fforms and apologise for getting caught
OL,12,Fup in the euphoria of our Copa America
OL,13,Fcelebrations. That video, that moment,
OL,14,Fthose words, do not reflect my beliefs
OL,15,For my character. I am truly sorry."
OL,17,FFernandez's French club-mate Wesley
OL,18,FFofana posted the video on his own
OL,19,Fsocial media accompanied by the
OL,20,Fmessage: "Football in 2024:
OL,21,FUninhibited racism."
