OL,3,CChelsea and FIFA investigating after
OL,4,CEnzo Fernandez posts 'offensive' video
OL,6,FChelsea released a statement on
OL,7,FWednesday morning welcoming
OL,8,FFernandez's apology, while announcing
OL,9,Fdisciplinary proceedings. Football's
OL,10,Fworld governing body FIFA said it too
OL,11,Fwas investigating.
OL,13,F"Chelsea Football Club finds all forms
OL,14,Fof discriminatory behaviour completely
OL,15,Funacceptable," the statement read.
OL,17,F"We are proud to be a diverse,
OL,18,Finclusive club where people from all
OL,19,Fcultures, communities and identities
OL,20,Ffeel welcome.
