OL,6,F"We acknowledge and appreciate our
OL,7,Fplayer's public apology and will use
OL,8,Fthis as an opportunity to educate. The
OL,9,Fclub has instigated an internal
OL,10,Fdisciplinary procedure."
OL,12,FA FIFA spokesperson said: "FIFA is
OL,13,Faware of a video circulating on social
OL,14,Fmedia and the incident is being looked
OL,15,Finto. FIFA strongly condemns any form
OL,16,Fof discrimination by anyone including
OL,17,Fplayers, fans and officials."
