OL,6,FThe statement read: "The president of
OL,7,Fthe French Football Federation,
OL,8,FPhilippe Diallo, condemns in the
OL,9,Fstrongest terms the unacceptable
OL,10,Fracist and discriminatory remarks
OL,11,Fwhich were made against the players of
OL,12,Fthe French team in the context of a
OL,13,Fsong sung by players and supporters of
OL,14,Fthe Argentina team after its victory
OL,15,Fin the Copa America and broadcast in a
OL,16,Fvideo on social media.
