OL,6,F"Faced with the seriousness of these
OL,7,Fshocking remarks, contrary to the
OL,8,Fvalues of sport and human rights, the
OL,9,Fpresident of the FFF decided to
OL,10,Fdirectly challenge his Argentinian
OL,11,Fcounterpart and FIFA, and to file a
OL,12,Flegal complaint for insulting remarks
OL,13,Fof a racist and discriminatory nature."
OL,15,FArgentina beat France in a penalty
OL,16,Fshoot-out in the 2022 World Cup final,
OL,17,Fa match around which some fans of the
OL,18,FArgentina team were heard to sing
OL,19,Fdiscriminatory songs.
